{"tid":1005692,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"惟恐車仔不亂 高圖爾斯勸夏神上「馬」","createTime":"2019-02-02T11:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T12:34:47.000Z","uid":1426,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ee6ef15fb158258661b7d994325e2a0b10c60b95","tid":1005692,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVTCEYb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVTCEYb.png&h=9bdd834a&s={SIZE}\" />車路士近況低迷，亦鬧出將帥不和的傳聞，其中一個與領隊沙利最貌合神離的，便是早前透過傳媒與這位意籍教頭隔空口水戰的夏薩特。此時，前車仔兼比利時國家隊隊友泰拔高圖爾斯，竟然在訪問中力勸夏神跟隨他，今夏一同效力皇家馬德里。<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，夏薩特一直嚮往轉投皇馬，加上最近沙利非常決絕地表示若對方想走，便絕不會留人，兩人之間的心病已漸漸浮上面。正當車仔周中大敗給般尼茅夫，更衣室一片混亂，去夏「落車」加盟皇馬的門將泰拔高圖爾斯，竟然惟恐不亂，放話明撬夏神。<br />\n<br />\n高圖爾斯接受比利時報章Het Nieuwsblad訪問時，談到皇馬要尋一個像基斯坦奴朗拿度級數的球員接班，他選擇了同為比利時同胞的夏薩特：「我喜歡他的踢法，也很想繼續與他同效一支球隊，但這是主席（佩雷斯）去決定的事，那不關我的事，我也不知道未來會發生甚麼。」<br />\n<br />\n高圖爾斯當然也不敢得罪目前皇馬的隊友：「其實球隊現在已很有質素，賓施馬最近狀態極佳，今季已轟入17球；加里夫巴利也是出色的球員，但必須要少一點傷患。」"},{"pid":"de9f90724aaa8197534de7595a5d79ebee3b929e","tid":1005692,"uid":1426,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/1940b0/f/800x0/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190202/large/1549097979_7edf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2F1940b0%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190202%2Flarge%2F1549097979_7edf.jpg&h=ae4531b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7caf3edf5359064354025d6e5afbbd7b6dd3c68","tid":1005692,"uid":36238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"人望高處 唔通留係度打歐霸咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2590840064035adf38aa55c7ac5c9cfd85ab9897","tid":1005692,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁撚反骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b60050995fa956d5aa065b2205f31dc95d09e4c","tid":1005692,"uid":112081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"25到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568b5022653b763958bfbfe467862e0b77fc589f","tid":1005692,"uid":63198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:56:34.000Z","msg":"邊個想成世留係次級聯賽?"},{"pid":"e69200de398c63802eb8ac62e51dc89c16c04e05","tid":1005692,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:57:07.000Z","msg":"牛唔飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8d59d8837bfc3e2ea8bd85aab2a91f99f6fefa","tid":1005692,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"依家佢個立場尷尬<br />\n<br />\n有件車仔過來的人  大家互相有個照應"},{"pid":"3d1ca0723045a6ccbc012f333bae201780122f34","tid":1005692,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"身為一個龍門場場失波都夠膽出黎9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24af6461d64f552297d8f3a0a82ff596324b879","tid":1005692,"uid":35547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"人地自己都講左好多年想去皇馬 洗撚你條25狗加把口講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76cd7e208430ee4f48ee1ed89bdebf54f3ece1e","tid":1005692,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.football.london/incoming/article15015304.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/0_Thibaut-Courtois.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.football.london%2Fincoming%2Farticle15015304.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs1200%2F0_Thibaut-Courtois.jpg&h=f1089472&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4fb278d8cbc4ac5a9b6039a7eb86cdd9346341c","tid":1005692,"uid":42246,"like":1,"d